snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls Online: Console Enhanced Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Experience Tamriel unleashed with Console Enhanced, a new version of the game for Xbox Series X|S that fully utilizes the native power of current-generation machines to provide incredible boosts to performance and graphical fidelity. Tamriel has never looked or played better on consoles with Console Enhance—available June 15 for Xbox Series X|S.

 https://www.xbox.com/games/elder-scrolls-online

Explore a world without limits and play your way in The Elder Scrolls Online, an ever-growing online saga set in the renowned universe of the Elder Scrolls. Join millions of players and tell your own story with your choice of fully customizable classes, action-packed combat, and hundreds of hours of adventure and exploration with no subscription required.
